    <string name="about_what_it_does">What the app does</string>
    <string name="about_does_1">Runs a local SOCKS5 proxy on 127.0.0.1:1080</string>
    <string name="about_does_2">Intercepts connections to Telegram IP addresses</string>
    <string name="about_does_3">Extracts DC ID from MTProto obfuscation init packet</string>
    <string name="about_does_4">Opens a WebSocket (TLS) connection to the corresponding DC via Telegram domains</string>
    <string name="about_does_5">If WS is unavailable (302 redirect) — automatically falls back to direct TCP</string>
