    <string name="onboard_title">Welcome to TG WS Proxy</string>
    <string name="onboard_step1_title">1. Start the proxy</string>
    <string name="onboard_step1_body">Tap the Start button on the Home screen to launch the local SOCKS5 proxy.</string>
    <string name="onboard_step2_title">2. Connect Telegram</string>
    <string name="onboard_step2_body">Tap "Connect in Telegram" — it will open Telegram with the proxy pre-configured. Confirm when prompted.</string>
    <string name="onboard_step3_title">3. Or add manually</string>
    <string name="onboard_step3_body">In Telegram: Settings → Data and Storage → Proxy → Add Proxy → SOCKS5\nServer: 127.0.0.1  Port: 1080\nLeave login/password empty.</string>
    <string name="onboard_done">Got it, let\'s go</string>
    <string name="telegram_not_installed">Telegram is not installed. Install Telegram, then open: Settings → Data and Storage → Proxy → Add Proxy → SOCKS5 (127.0.0.1:%1$d).</string>
